{"tid":494053,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔物獵人：世界》Beta版將於12月10日正式上線","createTime":"2017-12-09T08:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T13:22:53.000Z","uid":34186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f65b2449146f59865e2a78fe2a8c0c4406e66a3","tid":494053,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"今天遊戲Beta版預載已上架PSN港服，容量大小5.47GB，測試時間為期三天，僅限Plus會員與。<br />\n<br />\n在此次的beta版遊戲中，玩家可以體驗單人遊戲，以及最多4人同時進行的多人遊戲，透過三個任務內容體驗《魔物獵人：世界》的狩獵動作。<br />\n<br />\n能夠體驗的任務內容：<br />\n初級：狩獵大凶豺龍獵場：古代樹森林<br />\n中級：狩獵土砂龍獵場：大蟻塚荒地<br />\n上級：狩獵蠻顎龍獵場：古代樹森林<br />\n<br />\n在孕育豐富生態系統的新大陸，通過魔物的痕跡揭開世界面貌。當然除了武器、防具，各式各樣的生物、植物、地形等高密度的環境全部都能利用，展開全新的狩獵世界，想要提前親身感受的玩家千萬不要錯過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.playstation.com/zh-hant-hk/product/HP0102-CUSA09646_00-000000000000DEMO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.playstation.com%2Fzh-hant-hk%2Fproduct%2FHP0102-CUSA09646_00-000000000000DEMO&d=0f1PjH4DZh8cit4d2DdfqCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=dc594ccc\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.playstation.com/zh-hant-hk/product/HP0102-CUSA09646_00-000000000000DEMO</a>"},{"pid":"43e2aaebdae26e195d59d5d26afdd7ad8a436359","tid":494053,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:40:50.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddcb0e705aaeba7e83bab52b21590c568d9f73e","tid":494053,"uid":26030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"幾點玩得"},{"pid":"81355fc20d23842221817e459e8c3e2f968fe428","tid":494053,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾點玩得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1點am"}]}